Occasionally my cleric will get a &quot;your target is out of range&quot; trying to heal me when im standing right in front of her after I got feared.  Several weeks ago they were playing around with how often or the mechanics of player positions being reported to other players and the fact you go LD when feared is somehow causing an incorrect player position to be reported.  Been meaning to bug report that.  Other annoying side effect of this position filter tweak seems to be combat animations -- your group mates always seem to be running past a mob or spinning in place anymore. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://mywebpages.comcast.net/jwebb2/saraquael-art.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
