People see feared toons run away with a LD tag over the head.<br>
The feared player always see himself running away.<br>
<br>
If the feared player was moving when you got feared, then he will end up where the other players see him then.<br>
If he was standing still when he got feared, then he will see the view warp back to the origin of his fear-hit, but the server will still &quot;think&quot;  he is where his fear left him untill he moves.<br>
<br>
When the fear breaks on a player that did not move when the fear hit and he did not move to update the server, then the healers might get OOR and the player himself might get OORs too. <p><br>
